Use the [correct errors pattern](/patterns/error-validation) and show the error details above the postcode field.

### If the postcode is missing
Use “Enter a postcode”.

### If the postcode is not in a valid format
Use “Enter a valid UK postcode, for example, BB13 7HG”.

